file.name: UnexpectedError.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
UnexpectedError:
  type: object
  required:
    - status
    - message
  properties:
    status:
      type: integer
      format: int32
      description: |
        HTTP response codes:
        * `400` - Validation error (ex. invalid token)
        * `500` - An internal server error during processing
    message:
      type: string
      description: error message
